                        <a href="/ranges/elgrace_oh/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm font-bold rounded-lg border border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-200 transition text-center w-full">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-list-ul mr-1"></i> 施設詳細を見る
